posts.notes: My birthday is coming up in a few days and I'm nervous!
Today is my birthday. I didn't sleep too well because I was anxious about my plans for the afternoon. I'm looking forward to hanging out with friends!
Today was a great day so far! I slept a ton and there were birds outside chirping because of the nice weather.
Did you know that some animals live in shoes?
